    <text>
        <body>
        	<div1 type="letter">
        		<pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0371"/>
        		<head>Jim to Mademoiselle Marcelle Guerin <date value="06-27">June 27th</date></head>
        		
        		<opener>
            <dateline><date value="1916-06-27">June 27th</date></dateline>
            
            <salute>Dear Marcelle:</salute>
            </opener>
            
            <p>
            Thank you
            for your nice letter.
            I’m sorry your mother
            feels so run down.  I’m
            glad you’re taking her
            for a rest.
            </p><p>
            I inclose [sic] the 
            picture you ask for
            and you can keep it
            on condition that you’ll
            give me back the little
            one of myself in a 
            Bleriot.  I’ve tried to get
            
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0373" n="[p.2]"/>
            
            another with no success.
            Therefore the bribe.  I’ll
            try and get you an
            individual one of Chapman.
            </p><p>
            Where’s this bath 
            place you’re going to?
            </p><p>
            Kiffin has received
            his Croix and Medaille.
            </p><p>
            There has been no
            flying of late because
            of the weather, but I
            hope we can get started
            again to morrow.
            </p><p>
            I have an idea
                        
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0372" n="[p.3]"/>
            
            that we shall move
            from here before long
            for the north.
            </p><p>
            Don’t worry about
            the sort of letters you
            write me.  They can be
            sad or gay but it
            makes me happy either
            way for they are
            from you.
            </p><p>
            Kiffin, Johnson, Balsley
            and I passed “sergent”
            yesterday.  Fell quite
            important with the gold
            band on my kepi.
                        
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0374" n="[p.4]"/>
            
            Seems such a long, long
            time since I’ve seen you
            Marcelle.  Believe I’ll get 
            wounded so as to get
            a chance to see you again.
            </p><p>
            Excuse dull letter but
            I’m distracted to day.
            </p>
        		
        		<closer>
            <salute>My best</salute>
            
            <signed>Jim.</signed>
            
            <seg type="postscript">
            Do not put “Paris” after
            secteur postal.  Its just<lb/>
            Escadrille N. 124<lb/>
            S.P. 24
            </seg>
        		</closer>
        		
